th and projectile power.\n\nDino Roaryal is best played sitting. Standing positions are also okay but are not recommended as they limit the player's view. Dino Roaryal offers the player a different experience through the Oculus Goggles than the normal VR Pawn experience. ", "short_description": "Ride your chosen dinosaur and battle your way through the arenas. Overcome your enemies by using projectile attacks or physical tail attacks. "}]}, "developer_name": "KdanssLLC", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.traindz.com/dinoroaryal", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "KdanssLLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.traindz.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "2710427532541308"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1141512129892633"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "5557269174399628", "version": "1.0"}, "id": "868718174409506", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5528037507322795", "is_concept": false, "lates